Nxb2
{ The last sequence for Black wasn't that difficult to find but things remain extremely complicated. }
21. Rb1 Nc4+ 22. Kc1
{ After a long forcing line we've reached an imbalanced endgame which will most likely be a draw, but its imbalance could give dynamic chances for both sides. }
