{ White is ready to castle immediately. Black has many different setups here, which lead to very interesting positions. }
4... O-O { Castles is a very logical choice but White is slightly better. } 5.
a3 Bxc3+ 6. Qxc3 Nd5 7. Qd2 Nxf4 8. Qxf4 d6 9. Nf3 Nc6 10. e3
{ White is ready to finish development. It's still possible to castle queenside or kingside. The queen is actually strong on f4 and remains a threat to the black king. }
